# Terms and Conditions
## Definition

Before participating in any activity, the user must accept the Terms and Conditions.

## Rules

- Users who do not accept the Terms and Conditions cannot participate.

- Administrators can update the Terms and Conditions at any time.

- The Terms and Conditions are stored in a database table, and the most recent record is displayed to the user.

## Note

- This feature has now been implemented. Please verify that it is functioning as expected.

## Additional Note

- Ensure type safety, avoid production errors, follow best practices, and review the complete README.